00:00:13.018 --> 00:00:17.771
What are you going to cook?
Murmurala Upma (Puffed Rice Upma)

00:00:26.942 --> 00:00:29.104
Ingredients required to make Murmurala Upma

00:00:29.501 --> 00:00:43.183
Puffed Rice, Green Chillies, Curry Leaves, Onions, Peanuts, Carrots,
 Tomatoes, Coriander, Turmeric, Salt, Mustard Seeds, Cumin, Oil

00:00:53.489 --> 00:00:57.623
Take a pan and heat 2 tsp of oil

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:09.018
Add some mustard and cumin seeds

00:01:12.026 --> 00:01:17.039
Add 2 - 3 sliced green chillies

00:01:23.819 --> 00:01:27.009
Add some curry leaves

00:01:32.364 --> 00:01:39.428
Add some chopped onions and carrots

00:01:42.872 --> 00:01:46.833
Fry till the onions are a little brownish in color

00:01:48.326 --> 00:01:52.416
Add some turmeric powder

00:01:58.888 --> 00:02:07.269
Add a few peanuts and some chick peas

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:17.976
Add some chopped tomatoes

00:02:29.522 --> 00:02:37.297
Take a bowl of puffed rice and soak them in water for 2 mins
and then drain it out

00:02:53.668 --> 00:02:59.523
Add the soaked puffed rice into the pan

00:03:02.683 --> 00:03:06.226
Add some salt for taste

00:03:14.848 --> 00:03:20.595
Add 2 - 3 spoons of powdered peanuts

00:03:30.984 --> 00:03:35.096
Switch off the stove and add some coriander

00:03:40.094 --> 00:03:43.198
Take it into a serving bowl

